   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1901_AS_RBH_2_00045"/>Herrn Dr. <hi rend="latintype">Rich.
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb190427">I. Wollzeile 15</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1901_AS_RBH_2_00047"/><date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> ohne <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01175-1"/><unclear>Praejudiz</unclear><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01175-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L02968" subtype="Cf"/>.
               </note> für event.
               Eintritt werde ich heute Abend, am Ende<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon zum Nachtmahl, jedenfalls aber um
                  <time>10</time>, im <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01175-2"/><rs type="org" ref="#pmb169320" subtype="implied">Club</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01175-2"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" subtype="See" target="L01167"/>.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><p><rs type="person" ref="#pmb12740">Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav</rs> wohnt nach wie vor <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50825">Tief. Gr. 23</rs>; vielleicht i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t er aber in die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Tagen in
                  der <rs type="place" ref="#pmb44413">Brühl</rs></p></postscript></div>
      </body>
